@page
@model TripMatch.Pages.Shared.AboutUsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="aboutus-container">
    <div class="aboutus-box">
        <h2 class="aboutus-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Us</h2>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>TripMatch</strong>, your go-to platform for personalized travel experiences. We are passionate about helping travelers find the perfect destinations and travel plans that match their preferences and dreams.</p>

        <h3 class="aboutus-subtitle"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Our mission is to simplify the travel planning process by matching travelers with the best options available. Whether you're an adventurer, a family on vacation, or someone looking for a relaxing getaway, we have something for everyone.</p>

        <h3 class="aboutus-subtitle"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Our Vision</h3>
        <p>We envision a world where everyone can easily explore their dream destinations without the hassle of complicated planning. Our technology and expertise help travelers enjoy their journeys stress-free.</p>

        <h3 class="aboutus-subtitle"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Our Team</h3>
        <p>Our team is made up of seasoned travel experts, developers, and customer service professionals, all driven by the love for travel. We work hard to provide you with the best travel experiences.</p>

        <h3 class="aboutus-subtitle"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@tripmatch.com">support@tripmatch.com</a>. We’re here to help you make the most of your travel plans.</p>
    </div>
</div>